{"tid":2300614,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【暴政報告】初步調查結果27.2分　 創1999年有記錄以來新低","createTime":"2020-11-25T16:06:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T17:02:00.000Z","uid":290118,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"68e3975f630431e88a66d59e69d5f507fb1d955a","tid":2300614,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T16:06:33.000Z","msg":"來源：經濟日報<br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥今日公布任內第4份報告，香港民意研究所就施政報告作調查，以固網及手提電話，以及預先隨機抽樣樣本，一共訪問713人，初步結果是錄得27.2分，較去年下跌2.5分，並創下1999年有記錄以來新低。<br />\n<br />\n有51%受訪者，對施政報告非常不滿、13%受訪者稱幾不滿，對施政報告感到非常滿意，則只有6%的受訪者。不過，滿意率淨值為負45.5%，較去年上升2個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n以0至100分作評分，0為非常不滿、100分為非常滿意，今日的施政報告為27.2分，除了是林鄭月娥任內最低評分的一份施政報告，更是1999年有記錄以來新低，即林鄭月娥連續兩份施政報告創新低。"},{"pid":"8733c3c4c3479490f5ca76a79883b39fc39c34fc","tid":2300614,"uid":373469,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T16:11:54.000Z","msg":"下，咁都有廿幾分......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76487ce420ca01aae0a816c6e111860c42e76c1a","tid":2300614,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8733c3c4c3479490f5ca76a79883b39fc39c34fc","tid":2300614,"uid":373469,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T16:11:54.000Z","msg":"下，咁都有廿幾分......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T16:16:22.000Z","msg":"鑽石能量底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66ff312c349dca973caf76289f8ab86187cd07c0","tid":2300614,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T16:17:53.000Z","msg":"隻死賤婦唔係話冇嘢好挑剔咩"},{"pid":"efec50a671658be891bf6b2a94b9711b56ff00a0","tid":2300614,"uid":115579,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66ff312c349dca973caf76289f8ab86187cd07c0","tid":2300614,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T16:17:53.000Z","msg":"隻死賤婦唔係話冇嘢好挑剔咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T16:19:07.000Z","msg":"你地全部錯 我啱"},{"pid":"e079d85c1b04f382fc78c251320325b41cfab21b","tid":2300614,"uid":84176,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T16:22:11.000Z","msg":"對於個人評分一笑置之，嗤之以鼻"},{"pid":"2d9da9eee0f5a1efe4c1f8ad7199ad0d6f92d3aa","tid":2300614,"uid":117032,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T16:59:44.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母2.72分都卑撚多佢啦<br />\n<br />\n施政報告定係擦鞋報告呀？！仆街咁搞法同派哂啲錢上大劣有乜撚野分別"},{"pid":"e9e627646ea53e8923677224de5d77798e578895","tid":2300614,"uid":145923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T17:00:32.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"22f07408778fbc00c260cb215bccc2b69a45adac","tid":2300614,"uid":187537,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T17:01:06.000Z","msg":"咁垃圾都有27分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大灣區擦鞋報告，得罪晒黃藍兩邊"},{"pid":"6451cc310b325c41dd9f2adccff63fa08a7d7a85","tid":2300614,"uid":7855,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T17:02:00.000Z","msg":"睇完除左交通果part<br />\n成份都唔關自己事咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黃藍都嬲啦"}]}